messageBody:
Hello all

With all the conjecture that goes on about KR's thoughts about this or that, I thought it might be useful to upload a letter in KR's own QS hand, written to the letter writing circle in December 1969.

I am sorry that it is scanned from a rather poor photocopy (laser copies weren't around in those days) so some of it may be a bit difficult to read.  However, some of the letter may be pertinent to the discussions on dialect and pronunciation as well as giving an insight into KR's use of QS.

regards

.�H�\�K�W
